<section sectnbr = "5B">
<servcat sctnbr = "05" scnbr = "02">
<configtype typenbr = "0">
<servinfotype sitcode = "6">
<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "AENCP70A5206011" svcinfotypenbr = "08" svcinfoqualnbr = "01" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "1">
<title>
Manual Transaxle Unit Dismounting and Remounting
</title>
<servinfosub id = "AENCP70A5206011001">
<title>
Dismounting
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove battery and battery tray with ECM. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A1A06002"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove air cleaner assembly. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A1406004"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Disconnect back up light switch connector and release wiring harness clamps.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Disconnect gear shift and gear select control cables (1) from transaxle. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A5206005"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove clutch operating cylinder (2). 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A5306013"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A521056.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "72.944mm" ver = "01" gw = "160" gh = "190"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove ground cable from transaxle.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove engine undercovers.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Drain transaxle oil. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A5206002"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove starting motor. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A1906002"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove drive shaft assembly. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A3116003"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Open hood as wide as possible and hold it by using rope.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Hang up engine with chain (1) so that engine does not tilt.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A521061.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "62.506mm" ver = "01" gw = "226" gh = "161"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Support transaxle with transmission jack.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove transaxle-to-engine bolts (1) of upper side.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A521058.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "68.265mm" ver = "01" gw = "222" gh = "177"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove engine left mounting bracket (1).
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A521059.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "51.253mm" ver = "02" gw = "137" gh = "129"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove engine rear mounting bolts (3), transaxle-to-engine bolts (1) and nut (2) of lower side, and then lower transaxle.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A521062.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "116.955mm" ver = "02" gw = "235" gh = "315"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "4" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "0.865in"/>
<colspec colnum = "3" colname = "3" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "4" colname = "4" colwidth = "0.789in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
[A]:
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Right side
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
[B]:
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Left side
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AENCP70A5206011002">
<title>
Remounting
</title>
<attention2>
<ptxt>
Failure to take proper precautions when remounting the manual transaxle can cause damage to parts.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
When installing the transaxle, be careful not to let the drive shaft scratch the oil seal. Oil leaks may occur if the oil seal lip is scratched by the drive shaft.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Do not use a hammer when installing the drive shaft joint into the differential gear. Hitting the drive shaft joint with a hammer will damage the joint.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention2>
<ptxt>
Reverse dismounting procedure noting the following points:
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Tighten each bolt and nut to specified torque.
</ptxt>
</item>
<list2 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Manual transaxle: 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A5206010"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Front drive shaft: 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A3111001"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Starting motor: 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A1906002"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Engine left mounting bracket: 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A1406015"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Engine rear mounting: 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A1406015"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Air cleaner assembly: 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A1406004"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Clutch operating cylinder: 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A5306013"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
</list2>
<item>
<ptxt>
Set each clamp for wiring securely.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Fill with transaxle oil. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A5206002"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Connect battery and check function of engine, clutch and transaxle.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</servinfosub>
</servinfo>
</servinfotype>
</configtype>
</servcat>
</section></manual></suzuki>
